@{u}History@{uu}

   1.0a, Date 1.2.95
   - the 1.0 version was accidently compiled with the 68030 and 68881
     options of the oberon compiler. So MagicColors didn't run on
     stock A1200s. fixed.

   1.0, Date 7.7.94
   - first released Version

@EndNode

